Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.44,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,The moon's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.94,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.20,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,...a confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.43,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan, you're supposed to look at \Nthis person if you're confessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.07,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right, Hiro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:21.77,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise it's like I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:23.12,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:25.07,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confessing to both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:28.41,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I like Touko-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:29.96,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,and I like Hiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:33.22,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:35.87,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I finally said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.46,0:00:38.30,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Hiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:40.49,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,And I could say it to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:41.31,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.98,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,the moon's pretty today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:47.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan, I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:51.32,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-chan, let's stay good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:54.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:56.05,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,the moon's pretty today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:35.21,Episode-Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 10\N"Jonathan"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.29,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan seems so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.56,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan texts me every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:44.56,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,She does?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.34,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Saying, "For tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.60,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,For tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.45,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.70,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's for dinner today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.36,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Scooch, scooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.17,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagi-san was running today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:05.37,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Yana-chan's really hanging in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:08.66,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, have you told Touko already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:09.64,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.16,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Wait until after dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:14.97,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Tada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:17.72,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:19.62,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a bit too showy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.22,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-chan gave you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.97,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She told me Yukinari-san \Ncomplimented her in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.13,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I said I couldn't take it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:27.77,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Should I not have?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:31.16,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No, it looks nice on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:32.27,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.35,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:34.71,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Can I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.10,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Here, coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.73,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, when you're wearing that—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.39,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:46.24,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, Yanagi-san says she's \Ngoing to change into someone new.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.58,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-chan sure is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:58.48,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,A new Yana-chan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:00.77,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:06.05,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.61,Text1,Text,0000,0000,0000,,From: Sacchan\NSubject: For tomorrow\N"Tsuki wo Ageru Hito"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:49.72,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,"For tomorrow:"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:56.73,Text1,Text,0000,0000,0000,,From: Hiro Shirasaki\NRe: For Tomorrow\N"Meijinden" is amazing. It makes me \Nfeel really small, or really big.\NLooking forward to "Tsuki wo Ageru Hito"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.25,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Meijinden" is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:54.27,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.73,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,really small, or really big.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.66,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Looking forward to "Tsuki wo Ageru Hito,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:00.73,Italics,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:28.18,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:31.25,Italics,Kakeru 2,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hear the fragments \Nof the future anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.14,Italics,Kakeru 3,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.54,Italics,Kakeru 2,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because you met Touko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:39.10,Italics,Kakeru 3,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.63,Text1,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Inbox\NFrom: Yanagi\NSubject: Hinode-hama today\NClear skies today. Hinode Bridge, futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.48,Text1,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Inbox\NFrom: Yanagi\NSubject: Hinode-hama today\NSunny all day.\NIn front of the gelato store.\NBlacks 1, Whites 2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.52,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,"Blacks 1, Whites 2," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.49,Cover,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Issen Ichibyou Monogatari
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.45,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.23,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:38.63,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.01,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Oolong tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:42.00,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.21,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your blend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:48.77,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hot coffee in mid-summer. \NYou're totally a grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:50.34,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Her name was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.80,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Sachi Nagamiya, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:56.88,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,If you know where she lives, \NI want you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:07:00.55,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I can't tell you for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.92,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Figures. What do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:06.84,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Touko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.55,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You better be treating her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:11.49,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-san's really important to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:18.44,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you where Sacchan lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:22.83,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't answered anything \Nyou wanted to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:27.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really find the words,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.14,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't have to answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:44.24,Italics,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Clear skies today again. The sky is high.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:12.90,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.34,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Hiro Shirasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:21.85,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:37.28,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the 5:30 guy become a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:39.32,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:41.85,Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,You know something about this, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.66,Main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:47.49,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's my 5:30 girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:04.17,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me about the shiny things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.26,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yanagi-chan heard the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:08.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:12.22,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't taking care\N of Touko-chan at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:13.59,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.45,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Takayama said that to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:19.58,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,But does Fukami Touko\Nwant to be taken care of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:23.11,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,She makes me feel at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:24.33,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:27.77,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if she helps me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.69,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's helping me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:36.39,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I know more than
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:39.18,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,you do about the shiny thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.52,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.56,Main,Sachi,0000,0000,0000,,like Touko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:16.59,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.19,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:37.14,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:38.40,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.12,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:42.74,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who called \NKakeru the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:43.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.29,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:49.29,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, but what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.35,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Touko Fukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:53.50,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kakeru-kun home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:56.06,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, he's not home right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:10:58.53,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll be leaving then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.43,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're here, why not have \Na cup of tea or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:04.40,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to talk for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.57,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:06.28,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:13.07,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:13.69,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:18.78,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He's a strange kid, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.97,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:22.66,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:24.75,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.83,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:31.14,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm quite guilty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:32.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.06,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Can you move over a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.76,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You'll spill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:54.74,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:57.36,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't work when I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:00.11,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I hate the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:02.15,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Washing Japanese mustard spinach
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:04.65,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,in the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:07.32,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You've never done that, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:08.89,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.03,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru doesn't have\Na place to to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:15.94,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I've been dragging him around \Never since he was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:20.21,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We've only ever been in the same \Nplace for two years at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:24.12,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He was quick to make friends, \Nwhen he was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:27.18,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But as soon as there's \Na festival or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:30.22,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,all the kids go into festival mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.95,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,and they forget about Kakeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:36.10,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He had a phrase for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.11,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,"A sudden, expected loneliness."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:39.84,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Right, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.35,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:43.00,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:14.64,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.15,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:25.15,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You've been running the same \Nroute while I was gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.11,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:28.63,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:31.28,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,The seaside road is nice and windy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:35.34,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,It helps you recover, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:36.79,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:40.15,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Was the grandpa there at the snack shop today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.05,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:43.21,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That last uphill part,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:47.01,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,it's not even that bad, \Nbut it's tough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:52.22,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:54.44,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:56.79,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:04.74,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.98,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? So you were\Nquite a bookworm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:34.26,Main,Ossan,0000,0000,0000,,Back in the old days, everyone \Nread maybe twenty books a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.68,Main,Ossan,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we were being forced to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.81,Main,Ossan,0000,0000,0000,,So you couldn't really call me a bookworm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:42.63,Main,Ossan,0000,0000,0000,,So is your boyfriend being discharged?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.74,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, he can go back to work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:46.87,Main,Ossan,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:49.50,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, good for you, Nee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:52.56,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to invite him here sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:54.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.08,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You should tell Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:59.21,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,No, for coffee. Just coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.91,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming just to drink coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:05.84,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he said he couldn't \Nhave coffee in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.49,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,He really missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:08.38,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.19,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,So that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:11.84,Main,Momo,0000,0000,0000,,Tee hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:42.79,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,This is the town I grew up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:10.45,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Kakeru never had,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.85,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,a backdrop to my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:32.93,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Short-stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.75,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.20,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,They were such a pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:54.37,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,but now that I can't hear \Nthem, it's a bit lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:16:59.18,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Touko Fukami,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.66,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.70,Main,Yanagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're running again \Nstarting tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:13.26,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.11,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:44.40,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.64,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.14,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.62,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know about Kakeru-kun's
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.90,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,"sudden, expected loneliness."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:07.14,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:11.65,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:15.19,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:17.91,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:19.91,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You're not Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:20.66,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:24.38,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.34,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,They're missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.50,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,One's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.73,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:57.19,Italics,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not taking care of him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:06.97,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:13.88,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.60,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.62,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, you came here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.23,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought here I might
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:51.65,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,find out why I can't hear the \Nfragments of the future anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.17,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:56.00,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why you're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:57.99,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:02.05,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,about your "sudden, expected loneliness."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.26,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:05.92,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:09.43,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see the snow outside \Nthe window, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:11.55,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.19,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:18.40,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing a lot, and I'm inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:22.03,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a fragment. It's snowing all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.86,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.71,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.02,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.42,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:31.42,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,That's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.43,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:36.64,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,in the snow, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:39.46,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:41.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:45.93,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun... You kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:51.31,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.29,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.77,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it before, too. \NThat was the second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:59.48,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:02.52,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You said before that what we're seeing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:04.99,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,might not be the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:06.32,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.54,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that I'm seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:11.00,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Or will
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.32,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,that time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:15.12,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,come to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.55,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,True, what we've been seeing and hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:21.38,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,might not have been the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:25.98,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,But the view you're seeing\Noutside the window is winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:30.38,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake that we \Nheard and saw {\i1}something{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:32.57,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:36.74,Main,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,We have to accept that something is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:42.50,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:46.91,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,and if we do this, it'll make \Nit a fragment of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:31.72,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Kakeru-kun, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:34.39,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,We were together all day yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:37.56,Main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,That means the two of us are going to see \Nthe fireworks together again next year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:39.18,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:39.18,Episode-Title - Copy,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 11\N"Piano"
